Frequently Asked Questions

Is Rep.ai easy to set up?

Yes. Rep.ai’s AI Live Chat and AI Intent require a single script placed on your website. Then, tune the AI to your business through a few quick inputs. Rep.ai will scan your website and learn from your inputs, tailoring its conversation style and information accordingly.

Do visitors actually chat with Rep.ai?
How does Rep.ai know which company a visitor works at?
Does Rep.ai make mistakes?
Can I train Rep.ai to learn my business and product?
Can I restrict Rep.ai to only use knowledge of my business and product rather than external training data?
Can Rep.ai do AI video chat?
Does Rep.ai work on mobile?
